title: An Autistic College Student and her Sister with Cerebral Palsy

media:group.media:title: An Autistic College Student and her Sister with Cerebral Palsy
media:group.media:description:
Kaishawna is autistic and Nija is diagnosed with cerebral palsy. The two sisters, who were both born premature, were recently reunited after spending over a decade apart due to the adoption system. They are happy to be back together and are now learning how to build their relationship while accommodating one another.

Follow Kaishawna at https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-Tz7Lg6HZQEuE9jF-vj28Q
